race.description: Lucky 88 Racing Country Boosted Maiden Handicap
race.comment: DUBBO BOY (3) nice gelding ready to shed his Maiden status. Gripped on late when a sound second over 1010m at Moruya. Looking for this distance and no excuses from the barrier. DEEPLY (6) has come back a much stronger filly after the two good minor placings. Will relish the extra ground and has genuine top-three prospects. WIRE TO WIRE (11) resumes after having mixed luck last prep. Struggled to run the 1400m out when seventh over 1400m at Canberra on September 5. Gets the right run and can make his presence felt. SPLENDID MAGNUS (10) first run for the new yard she was beaten for early speed before warmed up late to run fourth over 1010m at Moruya. No surprise to see her figure in the money. BOUNDING BON (2) consistent gelding due for a change of luck fourth-up.
